  <brief_title>A Pilot Study to Determine the Impact of Clopidogrel (Plavix®) on Bleeding Associated With Punch Biopsies in Healthy Volunteers</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Pilot Study to Determine the Impact of Clopidogrel (Plavix®) on Bleeding Associated With Punch Biopsies in Healthy Volunteers</official_title>
  <sponsors>
