  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in the United States of America (USA). The aim of this trial is to
      determine the feasibility of demonstrating a quantifiable change from baseline in punch
      biopsy-induced bleeding durations and blood loss volumes in healthy subjects after receiving
      clopidogrel anti-platelet therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
